What Are Soft Skills?
1. Communication
2. Self-Motivation
3. Leadership
4. Responsibility
5. Teamwork
6. Problem Solving
7. Decisiveness
8. Ability to Work Under Pressure and Time Management
9. Flexibility
10. Negotiation and Conflict Resolution

